Gold key black is a key and reward from the Shades of Mort'ton minigame. To obtain it, the player must kill an Urium Shade and then burn its remains on a pyre. The key may be used to enter the Shade Catacombs and then open the correctly coloured chest. It will open a gold-framed chest with a black lock. This type of key can be used to open any door within the tombs, giving the player unrestricted access to all areas.

The following drop rates are provided by Jagex, unless otherwise specified.

Zealot robes[edit | edit source]

There is a 1/128 chance of hitting the zealot robes drop table. The player will obtain pieces in the following order, if they are not owned: boots, helm, robe bottom, and robe top. If the player owns all pieces, the rest of the drop table is rolled.
